.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
.sp
You can only set this parameter during start\-up and cannot change
this setting using the \fBsetParameter\fP database command.
.INDENT 7.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.nf
.ft C
mongos \-\-setParameter ShardingTaskExecutorPoolMaxSize=4
.ft P
.fi
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
.sp
